{"tid":949174,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"炭燒鰻魚飯","createTime":"2018-12-20T15:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T14:09:34.000Z","uid":175988,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c044ef9e5e9422f423ef4ce2a06b245e0a104d0d","tid":949174,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>名代宇奈とと @ 尖沙咀</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kWEsn07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkWEsn07.jpg&h=8c0c3002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>特大鰻魚丼</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鰻魚炭火香味突出，外層微焦脆口，色澤吸引<br />\n魚腩部位尚算厚肉肥美，有肉汁同魚油香<br />\n醬汁味道平衡，唔會過甜過膩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鰻魚幾多細骨，尤其係魚尾部份，又瘦又多骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n魚肉質地偏腍，唔夠彈性，應該唔係用野生鰻魚<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論：咁嘅份量 $150左右都可以接受，質素中等，如果唔使排隊可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"174bbd42003ef51d58ee8cfad53428bc8bafa001","tid":949174,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"要排隊就去日本食算<br />\n俾d賤民食cheap哂"},{"pid":"295cdb5d33cfe30a1540c16aaf3435e0561926f6","tid":949174,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/322872/dining/ad-hot-food/%e9%b0%bb%e9%ad%9a%e9%a3%af-%e4%b8%89%e6%b2%b3%e5%b1%8b-%e8%92%b2%e7%87%92/3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F322872%2Fdining%2Fad-hot-food%2F%25e9%25b0%25bb%25e9%25ad%259a%25e9%25a3%25af-%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%25b2%25b3%25e5%25b1%258b-%25e8%2592%25b2%25e7%2587%2592%2F3%2F&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9226fa65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/322872/dining/ad-hot-food/%e9%b0%bb%e9%ad%9a%e9%a3%af-%e4%b8%89%e6%b2%b3%e5%b1%8b-%e8%